   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support Education of Children With Special Needs</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In India a child born with special needs is destined for a life of dependency. For the poor this situation is extreme. The children with special needs are considered to be a social, financial, mental and physical burden to their families. Special Care Center annually reaches out to children who are hearing and speech impaired and mentally challenged and living in poor socio economic condition and is attended by 300 children who lack affordable education facility for their special needs.</narrative>
  </description>
